#
# To adopt upstream shape changes: bump this SHA, run
# `scripts/sync-backend-fixtures.sh`, and commit the regenerated fixtures
# together in one deliberate PR (expect internal/api's contract test to tell
# you if a load-bearing field stopped decoding).
#
# Format: the first non-comment, non-blank line is the ref (a full commit SHA
# preferred; a branch name works but reintroduces floating drift).
